WEBVTT

00:06:57.750 --> 00:07:00.636
ambako tutaangalia aina nyingine za uchafu

00:07:00.636 --> 00:07:02.121
ambazo zinaweza zikapunguzwa

00:07:02.121 --> 00:07:04.854
kutoka viwandani.

00:07:04.854 --> 00:07:08.859
uchafu katika miji, jinsi tunavyofikiri tunapoongelea uchafu,

00:07:08.859 --> 00:07:12.857
unakaribia asilimia tatu ya uchafu wote katika taifa

00:07:12.857 --> 00:07:15.244
ni takwimu za kushangaza.

00:07:15.244 --> 00:07:17.722
katika siku zako,

00:07:17.722 --> 00:07:19.248
katika maisha yako,

00:07:19.248 --> 00:07:22.276
utakapomwona mtu ambaye kazi yake ni

00:07:22.276 --> 00:07:25.419
kufanya usafi,

00:07:25.419 --> 00:07:27.908
chukua muda kuwatambua.

00:07:27.908 --> 00:07:32.500
chukua muda wako kuwashukuru.